@page "/rules"

<PageTitle>Rules</PageTitle>

<h1>Rule set</h1>
<p>
    The dashboard joins maintenance records, scores each machine with <strong>AI RulesEngine</strong> (weighted rules defined by Users),
    blends classifier trained on that joined data, and narrates the results.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Maintenance overdue past (and past double) the scheduled interval increases the risk score.</li>
    <li>Frequent and recurring breakdown tickets raise the urgency.</li>
    <li>High and moderate average downtime hours add weight.</li>
    <li>Repeated high-downtime parts signal potential supply chain or reliability issues.</li>
    <li>The model converts these joined features into a probability, blended 55% rules / 45% ML into the overall score.</li>
</ul>

<div class="card shadow-sm mt-4">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Severity guidance</h5>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Critical</strong> - immediate inspection and spare parts review.</li>
            <li><strong>High</strong> - schedule maintenance within one week.</li>
            <li><strong>Medium</strong> - monitor and plan service soon.</li>
            <li><strong>Low</strong> - continue routine checks.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
